# Higgsfield for RaapTech visuals

Prefer the **Higgsfield CLI** (`@higgsfield/cli`) for creating or regenerating
marketing imagery — same pattern as
[coleam00/ai-content-factory](https://github.com/coleam00/ai-content-factory):
explore cheap stills → human approve → spend video credits only on winners.

Read `.claude/skills/higgsfield/SKILL.md` before generating.

Optional MCP mirror: `.cursor/mcp.json` → `https://mcp.higgsfield.ai/mcp`
(OAuth). If MCP tools are unavailable, use the CLI.

## Brand constraints for prompts

- Industrial neo-brutalist RaapTech identity — shop floor, sheet metal, MEP,
  Autodesk Fabrication context. Real fabrication atmosphere, not SaaS gloss.
- Palette cues: warm concrete / paper (`#EDE9E0`), black ink (`#0B0B0C`),
  hazard orange (`#FF4D00`). Avoid purple gradients and soft glassmorphism.
- No AI-vendor logos or named AI product branding in the frame.
- Prefer full-bleed, edge-to-edge scenes suitable for hero backgrounds (16:9).

## Auth

```bash
higgsfield auth login
higgsfield account
```
